pageContext.claim: “I did something good. I made it famous. I made Juneteenth very famous. It’s actually an important event, it’s an important time. But nobody had heard of it. Very few people have heard of it.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump did not make Juneteenth, a holiday celebrated by American blacks, famous. He claims few people had heard of it but every year the Trump White House had issued a statement celebrating it.
